reviewText: Made me laugh watching old British stars !!
its ok but it lists full running time 90 mins but its not its got the same as the cut british version which can be bought cheaper

Another movie in the Confessions series.  This time around Timmy and his brother in law try to manage a pop group with Timmy taking over for the drummer.  Lots of nude cuties with a good amount of comedy.

The picture quality is excellent.  I played it in my blu ray player and only saw a few small drop outs.  Not bad for movie nearly 40 years old.
